BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8KCgcLq1rfpFcp5bL1LSK
SUMMARY:No Strings Attached: An Improvised Puppet Show for Grownups
DTSTAMP:20260411T111908Z
DTSTART:20260411T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s ORIGINAL improvised puppet show for grownups. An impr
	ovised fever dream with googly eyes and lots of laughter \\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAt
	 Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater\\\, puppets let their hair down (o
	r strings loose) in No Strings Attached—a hilarious\\\, adults improv pupp
	et show. After a long day entertaining the kids\\\, these puppets are read
	y to play—singing bawdy songs\\\, cracking jokes\\\, and getting up to all
	 kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call the shots with your 
	suggestions! \\nDon’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show at Pike Place Ma
	rket. It’s puppets\\\, it’s improv\\\, and it’s guaranteed to make you lau
	gh. \\nTHIS SHOW CONTAINS MATURE CONTENT\\\, LANGUAGE\\\, AND SITUATIONS\n
	\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/no-strings-attached-an-impro
	vised-puppet-show-for-grownups-4/2026-04-11/\n\nFrom Unexpected Production
	s
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/no-strings-attached-an-impr
	ovised-puppet-show-for-grownups-4/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:AbStcBiXdXeW8629Y23JW
SUMMARY:Taste of Improv - Improv Open Mic Georgetown Art Attack
DTSTAMP:20260411T111908Z
DTSTART:20260411T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a student\\\, a pro\\\, or just checking out the
	 Art Attack\\\, this is your chance to take the stage\\\, make bold choice
	s\\\, and have a blast doing it.\\nJoin Unexpected Productions Improv Scho
	ol as we join Georgetown’s ART ATTACK with a spontaneous showcase of impro
	v talent. Bring your squad\\\, support each other\\\, and celebrate the jo
	y of live\\\, unfiltered performance.\\nHit the Georgetown Art Attack\\\, 
	then head over to the Improv School.\\nCome for the art. Stay for the impr
	ov. See you there!\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/taste-of
	-improv-improv-open-mic-georgetown-art-attack-2-2-2-2/2026-04-11/\n\nFrom 
	Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/taste-of-improv-improv-open
	-mic-georgetown-art-attack-2-2-2-2/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Seattle Improv School\\\, 5700 6th Ave S\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98
	101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:qr2m6Dg7oiEEiOU5AvX94
SUMMARY:Seattle Suites: An Improvised Neil Simon Comedy
DTSTAMP:20260411T111908Z
DTSTART:20260411T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy in the style of Neil Simon\\\, where one hote
	l suite becomes a comedic pressure cooker for 3 hilarious improvised tales
	\\n\\n\\n\\nOne hotel suite. Countless misunderstandings. Relentless laugh
	s. \\nSeattle Suite is a laugh-driven\\\, fully improvised play inspired b
	y the style of Plaza Suite and California Suite\\\, capturing the signatur
	e humor of Neil Simon that is fast\\\, verbal\\\, and rooted in beautifull
	y human flaws. Each night\\\, a single Seattle hotel room becomes the sett
	ing for interconnected scenes inspired by your suggestions\\\, friends ove
	rshare and spiral\\\, romantic gestures go wrong\\\, awkward silences stre
	tch\\\, and small problems become big ones. The comedy comes from characte
	r and relationship\\\, building through sharp dialogue\\\, escalating tens
	ion\\\, and recognizable\\\, lived-in situations. Perfect for fans of smar
	t comedy\\\, relationship humor\\\, and classic theatrical wit.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvised-neil-sim
	on-comedy/2026-04-11/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvise
	d-neil-simon-comedy/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
